import React, {memo} from 'react'


import {HotRecommendWrapper, HotRecommendLeft, HotRecommendRight} from './style'
import RecConHeader from '@/components/rec-content-header' 

export default memo(function HotRecommend() {
  return (
    <HotRecommendWrapper className="w980">
      <HotRecommendLeft>
        <RecConHeader></RecConHeader>

      </HotRecommendLeft>
      
      <HotRecommendRight>

      </HotRecommendRight>
    </HotRecommendWrapper>
  )
})
